```
\\ Backend Environment File Example
PORT=5000
NODE_ENV=development

\\ Database (when adding database)
// DB_HOST=localhost
// DB_PORT=27017
// DB_NAME=ecommerce
// DB_USER=admin
// DB_PASSWORD=password

\\ API Keys (when adding payment/email services)
// STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=your_key
// SEND_GRID_API_KEY=your_key

\\ CORS Settings
ALLOWED_ORIGINS=http://localhost:3000
```
